<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>ParkerPixie — Sass, Shimmer & Sparkle</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Amigurumi. Design. Cozy Gaming. I’m Parker — the glitter behind ParkerPixie." />
  <style>
    :root{
      --brand:#8a5dff; --brand-deep:#4026a6; --ink:#1b1333; --bg:#fff; --muted:#6b5a8e; --gold:#f3d483;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box} body{margin:0;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Inter,Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:var(--bg)}
    a{color:var(--brand);text-decoration:none} a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;position:sticky;top:0;background:#fff}
    nav a{margin-left:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink)}
    .hero{max-width:1000px;margin:48px auto 24px;padding:0 20px;text-align:center}
    .eyebrow{letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);font-weight:700}
    h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4.5vw,44px);margin:10px 0 10px}
    p.lede{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto 22px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:#3b2e66}
    .cta{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:18px 0 26px}
    .btn{display:inline-block;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:14px;border:2px solid var(--brand);font-weight:700}
    .btn.primary{background:var(--brand);color:#fff;border-color:var(--brand)}
    .btn.ghost{background:#fff;color:var(--brand)}
    .caption{max-width:860px;margin:12px auto 36px;padding:12px 16px;border-left:4px solid var(--gold);background:#fff8e6;border-radius:10px;text-align:left}
    .grid{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto 60px;display:grid;gap:16px;padding:0 20px;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr))}
    .card{border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:16px;padding:18px 16px}
    .card h3{margin:0 0 6px}
    footer{border-top:1px solid #eee;padding:22px 24px;text-align:center;color:#6a6383}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/" aria-label="ParkerPixie" style="font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);">ParkerPixie</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="/about/">About</a>
      <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">Sass • Shimmer • Sparkle</div>
      <h1>Amigurumi. Design. Cozy Gaming.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        I’m Parker — the glitter behind ParkerPixie. Explore plush friends, brand glow-ups, and comfy content —
        all tied together with recovery, kindness, and a dash of chaos.
      </p>
      <div class="cta">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Commission an Amigurumi</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/about/">Who is ParkerPixie?</a>
      </div>

      <figure class="caption">
        <figcaption>
          ✨ “This is my happy place — our family cabin on the lake. I’m either crocheting with my capy crew,
          sneaking in some SteamDeck time, or playing with graphic design between kayaking, swimming, tubing,
          and boating. It’s where the sass, shimmer, and sparkle refill my soul.”
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Amigurumi Gallery</h3>
        <p>Whimsical capybaras, puffins, peacocks, and friends. Soft, cozy, and full of heart.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Graphic Design</h3>
        <p>Before/after glow-ups, social sets, and brand kits that shimmer in the feed.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Gaming</h3>
        <p>Cozy streams, guides, and builds inspired by Infinity Nikki &amp; Dreamlight vibes.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>© ParkerPixie · Made with glitter &amp; love</footer>
</body>
</html>
